name: Eating Baba Yaga DVD
description: Eating Baba Yaga: An Evening with Brian Rohr This Storytelling DVD consisting of two stories (16 minutes and 38 minutes respectively) and teachings about these stories and how they relate to our lives. The back cover of the DVD says: “In his show, Eating Baba Yaga, Brian invites the listener to that wild, gentle and fierce place that is known when confronting our Wyrd - our own unique and personal life path - and see how, through compassion, cunning and grace, we can engage those parts of our lives that may seem to want to destroy us, but in fact want us to become the adults we were always meant to be.” 71 minutes/Color
